Added method that creates optimized portfolio calculations and json to be sent to Website javascript backend

Data flow pipeline for aggregating stock price data daily
Added azure bing search api functionality, added high low opening price , added airflow only method
Added last plotting feature for portfolio, need to stage to connect to db and retrieve data
Added code for portfolio optimization , still need to add additional graphs
preparing to remove images col
Added additional filename param to grab_images, and cleaned some column names up
testing commit, incompelte markowitz portfolio opt script
Updated requirements.txt
Added dummy table creation in create_tables.py and added percentage change column in stock data method and put string metrics for sentiment
Added vanilla sentiment analysis method
Revamped stock data grabber to now have arguments for start and end dates, also renamed it for clarity
Forgot load_dotenv() method to grab mongo credentials
Method for creating collections table which holds tickers, company name and company logo into mongodb
Added edge case for stock data, modified image getting params, added load_to_db function, changed a dataframe key to uppercase
Swapped if/else for try/except, changed file naming structure
updated dependencies
Rebased image grabber , more concise than before
